<h1>Trends in Web Applications</h1>
<!-- Slides for a brief presentation -->

<slide>
</slide>

<slide><h2>What is a Web Application?</h2>
<ul>
  <li> Web site or part of a web site
  </li>
  <li> Performs some distinct function, e.g.
       <ul>
	 <li> maintaining a calendar
	 </li>
	 <li> ordering groceries
	 </li>
	 <li> controlling a printer
	 </li>
       </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
</slide>

<slide><h2>Widening Range of Platforms</h2>

<p> <strong>platform = ( server, OS, language )</strong> 
</p>
<p> <img src="Images/widening.png" />
</p>
</slide>

